name: IQ Backoffice
overview:
I.Q. BackOffice, LLC operates as a business process outsourcing company offering accounts payable, accounts receivable, and other accounting outsourcing solutions. Its accounts payable solutions include invoice receipt, approval and matching, exception processing, disbursement, and vendor relations. The companyâ€™s accounts receivable solutions include billing, lockbox, and cash application, exception management, and customer relations. It also offers accounting solutions, including finance and accounting, such as billing and accounts receivable, accounts payable, project/job accounting, fixed assets and inventory, general ledger, financial statement preparation and analysis, management reporting, budgeting, commissions, credit and collections, and banking and cash management, as well as human resources, including payroll, timekeeping, and employee business expenses. The company has strategic partnerships with Net Results Group, Inc. and Vengroff Williams & Associates, Inc.

I.Q. BackOffice, LLC is headquartered in Encino, California with additional offices in the United States, Canada, and India. I.Q. BackOffice, LLC operates as a subsidiary of R.C. Baral & Company, Inc.
